Do the safety exercises properly!

00:59:22.038 --> 00:59:26.960
THE DREAM LIFE OF MR. KIM

00:59:57.449 --> 00:59:59.784
A ladder with no work platform
is a safety rule violation.

00:59:59.868 --> 01:00:01.703
I said to clean up!

01:00:02.370 --> 01:00:05.874
I've been hearing whispers
about Mr. Kim coming back.

01:00:05.957 --> 01:00:07.292
Why would Mr. Kim make that list?

01:00:07.375 --> 01:00:08.251
VOLUNTARY RETIREMENT

01:00:08.335 --> 01:00:10.462
You've never given a damn
about the factory.

01:00:10.545 --> 01:00:12.797
-What's with the sudden change?
-I'm just doing my job.

01:00:12.881 --> 01:00:14.257
SAFETY VIOLATIONS

01:00:14.341 --> 01:00:16.301
Would writing up that list
bring him back to HQ?

01:00:16.384 --> 01:00:18.303
You might as well be the errand boy.

01:00:18.386 --> 01:00:20.100
-What else would you do?
-You little bastard.

01:00:20.200 --> 01:00:22.390
Let's do some work.
Leave if you don't want to.

01:00:22.474 --> 01:00:23.600
Hello, Mr. Kim.

01:00:23.683 --> 01:00:26.519
And try to hang on to your job
for as long as you can.

01:00:26.603 --> 01:00:28.021
That's what being a parent is.

01:00:28.104 --> 01:00:30.315
Come to headquarters
and bring your report.

01:00:30.398 --> 01:00:31.816
You call this "work"?

01:00:31.900 --> 01:00:33.860
And no matter how I look at it…

01:00:34.945 --> 01:00:36.947
it doesn't feel like work.

